Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch  Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch def similarity_dog_category(img_path):
    # 1. 
    detected_dog_face = dog_detector(img_path)
    detected_human_face = face_detector(img_path)
    
    # 2. 
    if detected_dog_face or detected_human_face:
        similar_dog_category = reconigze_dog_category(img_path)
    
    # 3. 
    describe = ""
    if detected_dog_face:
        describe = "hello dog, you look like a " + similar_dog_category
    elif detected_human_face:
        describe = "hello humman, you look like a " + similar_dog_category
    else:
        describe = "sorry, unrecoginze any human or dog, please change you input img."
    
    return describe
